{"timestamp": "2025-12-12 19:07:11.588896", "event": "llm_end", "text": "**What we see**\n\n| Test | Result | Interpretation |\n|------|--------|----------------|\n| `host_1_1_1_1` → `10.1.1.1` (gateway) | **Success** | Host 1 can reach its own subnet’s gateway. |\n| `host_2_1_1_1` → `10.1.1.1` (gateway) | **Success** | Host 2 can reach its own subnet’s gateway. |\n| `host_1_1_1_1` → `10.2.1.2` (host 2) | **Destination Host Unreachable** (from 10.1.1.2) | Host 1 cannot reach the other subnet. |\n| `host_2_1_1_1` → `10.2.1.2` (host 1) | **Timeout** | Host 2 cannot reach the other subnet. |\n| `host_2_1_1_1` → `10.1.1.1` | **Success** | Host 2 can reach its own gateway. |\n\nBoth hosts have correct IPs, netmasks, and default routes:\n\n* `host_1_1_1_1` – 10.2.1.2/24 → default via 10.2.1.1  \n* `host_2_1_1_1` – 10.1.1.2/8 → default via 10.1.1.1  \n\nThe problem is strictly **inter‑subnet** traffic (10.1.1.0/8 ↔ 10.2.1.0/24).  \nThe gateway on each subnet (10.1.1.1 and 10.2.1.1) can reach the other subnet’s gateway, but packets are not being forwarded between the two networks.\n\n**Where the failure is**\n\nThe network devices that should provide routing between the two subnets are not running:\n\n* `switch` – “Device `switch` is not running.”  \n* `router` – “Device `router` is not running.”\n\nBecause the switch/router is down, the gateways on each subnet cannot forward packets to the other subnet, so all cross‑subnet traffic is dropped.\n\n**Root cause**\n\nThe router (and its connected switch) is not powered on / not running, so the default gateways on each subnet cannot forward traffic between the 10.1.1.0/8 and 10.2.1.0/24 networks.\n\n**Next steps (if you want to fix it)**\n\n1. Power on / start the `switch` and `router` devices.  \n2. Verify that the router’s interfaces are up and that routing is configured correctly (e.g., `frr_show_running_config`, `frr_show_ip_route`).  \n3. Once the router is operational, re‑test cross‑subnet pings; they should succeed.", "generation_info": {"model": "gpt-oss:20b", "created_at": "2025-12-12T19:07:10.351154387Z", "done": true, "done_reason": "stop", "total_duration": 12858804406, "load_duration": 75119014, "prompt_eval_count": 7763, "prompt_eval_duration": 313451338, "eval_count": 1112, "eval_duration": 10741810138, "model_name": "gpt-oss:20b"}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7763, "output_tokens": 1112, "total_tokens": 8875}}
